    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust E46 M3, powered by the high-strung S54 3.2L atmospheric inline-six. This engine features individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, providing an exceptional power band peaking at an 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a mechanical limited-slip differential. Critical enthusiast-grade maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a cooling system refresh. While the exterior shows minor cosmetic patina from spirited use, the chassis remains sharp with refreshed bushings and a responsive suspension geometry. This is a visceral, driver-oriented machine that performs exactly as an M-car should.",
