      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2012 Porsche 911 Carrera in Basalt Black Metallic over a Luxor Beige leather interior. This car represents the ideal 'driver\u2019s example': it is mechanically superb and aesthetically sharp, showing only the honest signs of a well-loved life on the road. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like finish, though a discerning eye will find minor stone chips on the front valence consistent with highway touring. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the leather is supple, the dash is free of sun damage, and every toggle and switch operates with German precision. Recent preventative maintenance includes a full PDK service, new spark plugs, and a fresh set of Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires. It comes with a complete binder of service records and two keys. This 911 is ready for the coast or the commute without a moment's hesitation.",
